title: Street Dogs Of South Central.mp4
description:
This is the FULL version of the documentary "Street Dogs Of South Central" which aired in 2013. I searched online for the whole thing, but all I could find was part 1. Part 2 was nowhere to be found. So I requested the movie from the maker himself, and he sent it to me for free, then I ripped it from the DVD. This is as long as most movies, an hour and a half. 

I've seen people on different torrent sites requesting part 2. This contains part 1 and 2.

I recommend this to all animal lovers, as it shows how hard these dogs have it, surviving on the streets. Please, adopt from a shelter instead of buying a dog. Too many shelter dogs (and cats) are killed every year.

Enjoy!!

By the way, this is my first torrent upload ever, so if something is wrong, please give me some tips
